<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi> kulottuṅkacoḻatevaṟku yāṇṭu patiṉālāvatukketirāmāṇṭu pe
<lb n="2" break="no"/><unclear>rumāḷ</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="6" unit="character"/> Aviṉāciyāṉa viratamiṭṭamālaiyeṉ Āḷuṭaiyār Aviṉāciyāṇṭāṟku vaitta ca
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ntiyātipam Onṟukkup pon kaḻaiñcum kuṭaṅkoṇṭu koyil pukuvāṉe celuttuvāṉāka kuṭut <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="4"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> veṭṭivicceṉ Uyyavantāṉ Aviṉāciyeṉ Itu cantirātittavaṟ celvatākap paṉ
<lb n="5" break="no"/>mā<hi rend="grantha">heśvara rakṣai <g type="ddanda">.</g></hi>
